description=Collectible retro game consoles and cartridges. Find NES, SNES, Genesis, Game Boy, Atari 2600, Game Gear, and Master System consoles during loot runs. Play real retro games on in-game TVs powered by libretro emulation. Place your own legally obtained ROM files in your Zomboid/PZEMU/roms/ directories (nes/, snes/, genesis/, gb/, atari2600/, gg/, sms/). For dumping ROMs from original cartridges, we recommend the Retrode hardware device. Linux and Windows supported.
